A surreal melted art style depiction of our favorite couple in a fall festive atmosphere. The bombshell blonde glows with elegance, her form slightly dripping and morphing like melting wax, dressed in a warm autumn-toned outfit that flows into the scenery. Beside her, the bald man with a trimmed beard and sunglasses stands strong yet fluid, his body melting into the golden leaves and flickering lantern light. Around them, pumpkins, hay bales, and glowing candles distort and stretch like liquid colors, blending with the couple as if they are part of the festival itself. A dreamlike sky of molten orange, crimson, and amber cascades above, while their white wolf companion shimmers and warps, its fur flowing like melted silver in the moonlight. The scene radiates romance and surreal beauty, a festival of autumn dripping into fantasy.
